The legal status of [[drugs]] and [[drug precursors]] varies substantially from country to country and is still changing in many of them. United Nations classify drugs internationally, it affects all its [[Member states of the United Nations|member states]].
==Territories== {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Territory ! Drug and precursor laws<!-- many laws cover both precursors and drugs themselves --> |- ! United Nations | * INCB – ''[[Single Convention on Narcotic Drugs]], 1961''<ref>{{cite web|title=1961 Convention|url=http://www.incb.org/incb/en/narcotic-drugs/1961_Convention.html|website=www.incb.org}}</ref> * INCB – ''[[Convention on Psychotropic Substances]], 1971''<ref>{{cite web|title=Convention on Psychotropic Substances|url=https://www.unodc.org/unodc/en/treaties/psychotropics.html|website=www.unodc.org}}</ref> * INCB – ''[[United Nations Convention Against Illicit Traffic in Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances]], 1988''<ref>{{cite web|title=Convention against the Illicit Traffic in Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances|url=https://www.unodc.org/unodc/en/treaties/illicit-trafficking.html|website=www.unodc.org}}</ref> ** INCB "Green list" – ''List of Psychotropic Substances under International Control''<ref>{{cite web|title=green-lists|url=https://www.incb.org/incb/en/psychotropic-substances/green-lists.html|website=www.incb.org}}</ref> ** INCB "Yellow list" – ''List of Narcotic Drugs under International Control''<ref>{{cite web|title=Yellow list|url=https://www.incb.org/incb/en/narcotic-drugs/Yellowlist_Forms/yellow-list.html|website=www.incb.org}}</ref> * ''[[Chemical Weapons Convention]], 1997'' * ''[[UN Convention on Drug Precursor Chemicals]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=UN Convention on Drug Precursor Chemicals|url=http://www.chemsafetypro.com/Topics/Convention/UN_Convention_Drug_Precursor_Chemicals.html|website=www.chemsafetypro.com|language=en}}</ref> ** INCB "Red list" – ''List of Chemicals frequently used in the Illicit Manufacture of Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances under International Control''<ref>{{cite web|title=green-lists|url=https://www.incb.org/incb/en/psychotropic-substances/green-lists.html|website=www.incb.org}}</ref> |}
==Countries== {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Country ! Drug and precursor laws<!-- many laws cover both precursors and drugs themselves --> |- ! [[Drug policy of Germany|Germany]] | * Anlage I<ref>{{cite web|title=(nicht verkehrsfähige Betäubungsmittel)|url=https://dejure.org/gesetze/BtMG/Anlage_I.html}}</ref> * Anlage II<ref>{{cite web|title=(verkehrsfähige, aber nicht verschreibungsfähige Betäubungsmittel)|url=https://dejure.org/gesetze/BtMG/Anlage_II.html}}</ref> * Anlage III<ref>{{cite web|title=(verkehrsfähige und verschreibungsfähige Betäubungsmittel)|url=https://dejure.org/gesetze/BtMG/Anlage_III.html}}</ref> |- ! [[Drug policy of Sweden|Sweden]] | * ''[[:sv:Narkotikastrafflagen|Narkotikastrafflagen]]'' ** ''Läkemedelsverkets föreskrifter om förteckningar över narkotika''<ref>{{cite web|title=Läkemedelsverkets föreskrifter - LVFS/HSLF-FS - Läkemedelsverket / Medical Products Agency|url=https://lakemedelsverket.se/overgripande/Lagar--regler/Lakemedelsverkets-foreskrifter---LVFS/|website=lakemedelsverket.se|language=sv}}</ref> * [[:sv:Lagen om förbud mot vissa hälsofarliga varor|''Lagen om förbud mot vissa hälsofarliga varor'']] ** List of substances<ref>{{cite web|title=Förordning (1999:58) om förbud mot vissa hälsofarliga varor|url=http://www.notisum.se/rnp/sls/fakta/a9990058.HTM|website=www.notisum.se}}</ref> * [https://mpa.se/malgrupp/Foretag/Narkotikakemikalier/ Kontroll av narkotikaprekursorer] (up to date list of laws) |- ! New Zealand | [http://www.medsafe.govt.nz/profs/class/classintro.asp Search engine] |- ! [[Drug policy of the United Kingdom|United Kingdom]] | * ''[[Medicines Act 1968]]'' * ''[[Misuse of Drugs Act 1971]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=The Misuse of Drugs Act 1971 (Ketamine etc.) (Amendment) Order 2014|url=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2014/1106/made|website=www.legislation.gov.uk|language=en}}</ref> * ''Misuse of Drugs Regulations 2001'' * ''[[Drugs Act 2005]]'' * ''[[Psychoactive Substances Act 2016]]''<ref>{{cite web|title=Psycho