{{GeoGroupTemplate}} This is a '''list of [[airport]]s in [[Saint Pierre and Miquelon]]''', sorted by location.
Saint Pierre and Miquelon is an [[overseas collectivity]] ({{lang-fr|collectivité d'outre-mer}}, or ''COM'') of [[France]], consisting of several small [[island]]s off the eastern coast of [[Canada]] near [[Newfoundland and Labrador|Newfoundland]].
