'''Masarrochos''' is a village in the district [[Pobles del Nord]] in the municipality of [[Valencia]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.valencia.es/ayuntamiento/ayuntamiento.nsf/vDocumentosTituloAux/Pedan%C3%ADas?opendocument&nivel=2_7&lang=1|title=Ayuntamiento de Valencia. Pedanías. Alcaldías de Barrio|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-09-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.valencia.es/ayuntamiento/webs/estadistica/Cartografia/Dt17_Pobles_Nord.pdf|title=DT17.mxd|last=|first=|date=|website=|language=Spanish|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-09-24}}</ref> The locality has a population of 2,319.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ine.es/dyngs/INEbase/en/operacion.htm?c=Estadistica_C&cid=1254736177010&menu=resultados&idp=1254734710990|title=INEbase / Demography and population /Municipal Register. Population by municipalities /Nomenclature: Continuous Register Population by Population Unit / Results|website=www.ine.es|language=en|access-date=2018-09-24}}</ref>

